        <updateDate>2019-09-06T18:25:25Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Return Expenses Paid and Yielded Act or the REPAY Act</b></p> <p>This bill modifies certification and reporting requirements relating to certain sales of major defense equipment. It requires a review and report on options for expansion of the use of administrative surcharges under the foreign military sales program, monitoring on the performance of such program, and a report and briefing for determining the future-year needs for administrative surcharges under such program. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
